    "patch_code": "private double calculateAsymptoticPValue(double Umin,\n                                        int n1,\n                                        int n2)\n        throws ConvergenceException, MaxCountExceededException {\n\n    long n1L = n1;\n    long n2L = n2;\n    \n    double n1n2Prod = n1L * n2L;\n\n    if (Double.isInfinite(n1n2Prod)) {\n        throw new ArithmeticException(\"Underflow during calculation\");\n    }\n\n    // http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mann%E2%80%93Whitney_U#Normal_approximation\n    double EU = n1n2Prod / 2.0;\n    double VarU = n1n2Prod * (n1 + n2 + 1) / 12.0;\n\n    if (Double.isNaN(VarU) || Double.isInfinite(VarU)) {\n        throw new ArithmeticException(\"Underflow during calculation\");\n    }\n\n    double z = (Umin - EU) / FastMath.sqrt(VarU);\n\n    final NormalDistribution standardNormal = new NormalDistribution(0, 1);\n\n    return 2 * standardNormal.cumulativeProbability(z);\n}",
