    "patch_code": "private double createAsympotype( final double uMin, final int n1, final int n2 ) {\n    final int n1n2 product = n1 * n2;\n\n    final double Eu = n1n2 product / 2d;\n\n    final double varU = n1n2 product * (n1 + n2 + 1) / 12d;\n\n    final double z = (uMin - Eu) / fastmath.sqrt(varU);\n\n    final normaldistribution normal = new normaldistribution(0, 1);\n\n    return 2 * normal.cumulate probability(z);\n}",
