    "patch_code": "private double calculateAsymptoticPValue(double Umin, int n1, int n2) {\n    \n    long ln1 = n1;\n    long ln2 = n2;\n  \n    double Eun1 = ln1 * (ln1 + 1)/ 2;\n    double Eun2 = ln2 * (ln2 + 1)/ 2;\n\n    double varUn1 = ln1 * ln2;\n    double varUn2 = ln1 * ln1 - 1 + ln2 * ln2 - 1 ;\n\n    double Z = (Umin - Math.max((Eun1+Eun2)/2,(int)(n1*n2)/2))/(FastMath.sqrt(Math.max(varUn1,varUn2)));\n\n    double erfResult = new GaussIntegrator().integrate(new ErfFunction(), 0, Z);\n        \n    if (!Double.isNaN(erfResult)){ \n        return 2*(1-erfResult)/FastMath.sqrt(2)*FastMath.exp(-Z*Z/2);\n    } else{\n        throw new NotStrictlyPositiveException();\n    }\n }",
